divs: Sighting DetailsI saw two sets of strange clouds formations when stopped at a stop sign. I grab my phone and took a photo on my Blackberry. Over a month later I transferred the photo to my PC. It was then that I noticed a set of dark objects in the same format as the set of two strange cloud objects. (see Photo)
Summary: Just noticed the pair of dark objects after blowiog up the photo of the set of two strange cloud objects
